yingyinNormal.en: It's a long trip to deliver this in person.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这么大老远亲自送来啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Girls, let's go. Time to deliver the cookies!
yingyinNormal.zh: 姑娘们 出发了，送饼干去喽

yingyinNormal.en: To preserve, package and deliver. That is legal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 保存，包装，传送，这是合法的。

yingyinNormal.en: Father Christmas just has a few more presents to deliver.
yingyinNormal.zh: 圣诞老人还有几样礼物要送。

yingyinNormal.en: Father Christmas just has a few more presents to deliver.
yingyinNormal.zh: 圣诞老人还有几样礼物要送。

yingyinNormal.en: And I only had a few more to deliver. To Suzy Sheep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还有几样礼物要送。小羊苏西！

yingyinNormal.en: When I deliver. $500 per unit and you've got a deal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我交货的时候每台给我500美元我们就成交了。

yingyinNormal.en: Do you think that you can just deliver me like a package?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你以为，你能把我当个货物，运过去吗？

yingyinNormal.en: We're not going to deliver cookies until we do dance class.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不上完舞蹈课 我们是不会去送饼干的

yingyinNormal.en: How? If I deliver, will you keep me on? You tell me how first.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么做？如果我做到，你能让我留下吗？你得先告诉我。

yingyinNormal.en: No. My orders were to deliver you information regarding the Syndicate.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不干，我的任务是带给你关于辛迪加的情报。

yingyinNormal.en: But, Attinger, buddy, for both our sakes, you need to deliver the Seed.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可是艾汀杰为了我们两个好，你必须给我说好的种子。

yingyinNormal.en: That's fantastic. Wonderful. But we're going to deliver cookies! Come on!
yingyinNormal.zh: 太好了 非常棒。但我们要去送饼干了！来吧！

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Zebra is going to bed now. He has to get up early to deliver the post.
yingyinNormal.zh: 斑马爸爸现在要上床睡觉了。他必须早早起床去送信。

yingyinNormal.en: And how many pizzas do you usually deliver? Oh, 30, 40 pizzas per night. Wow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那你一般能送几个披萨？一晚上三四十个。喔 。

yingyinNormal.en: I am confident. Surely. I think the taste will deliver. The health aspect for sure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我很有信心。我认为味道说明一切。在健康方面肯定没问题。

yingyinNormal.en: If Simms could deliver two or three delegates... That could push Kansas over the edge.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果西姆斯可以拉来两三名代表…那就能整个拿下堪萨斯了。

yingyinNormal.en: And I only had a few more to deliver. To Suzy Sheep, Danny Dog, Pedro Pony. That's easy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我还有几样礼物要送。小羊苏西，小狗丹尼，小马佩德罗。那很简单！

yingyinNormal.en: Sir, when it comes to Matthews, I don't believe he'll deliver. Let's take this from his hands.
yingyinNormal.zh: 总统阁下，马修斯那边，我觉得他不会照办。我们夺下主动权吧。

yingyinNormal.en: No man in the sky intervened when I was a boy to deliver me from daddy's fist and abominations.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我小时候天上可没人来干预，没人把我从我爸的拳头和恶性之下解救出来。
